---
title: BeaconLink Deployment Rollback Flow
---

flowchart TB

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deployment Execution
    %% =====================================================

    Deployment["Deployment Revision"]

    Execution["Deployment Execution"]

    Deployment --> Execution

    %% =====================================================
    %% Validation
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Validation["Post-Deployment Validation"]

        Health["Health Checks"]
        Readiness["Readiness Verification"]
        Metrics["Performance Metrics"]
        Policies["Policy Compliance"]
        Drift["Drift Detection"]

    end

    Execution --> Health
    Health --> Readiness
    Readiness --> Metrics
    Metrics --> Policies
    Policies --> Drift

    %% =====================================================
    %% Decision
    %% =====================================================

    Decision{"Deployment Healthy?"}

    Drift --> Decision

    %% =====================================================
    %% Success Path
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Success["Successful Deployment"]

        Promote["Promote Revision"]
        Inventory["Update Inventory"]
        AuditSuccess["Audit Success"]
        EventsSuccess["Publish Success Events"]

    end

    Decision -->|Yes| Promote

    Promote --> Inventory
    Inventory --> AuditSuccess
    AuditSuccess --> EventsSuccess

    %% =====================================================
    %% Rollback Path
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Rollback["Rollback Process"]

        Detect["Failure Detected"]

        Freeze["Freeze Rollout"]

        Select["Select Previous Stable Revision"]

        Generate["Generate Rollback Plan"]

        Dispatch["Dispatch Rollback Tasks"]

    end

    Decision -->|No| Detect

    Detect --> Freeze
    Freeze --> Select
    Select --> Generate
    Generate --> Dispatch

    %% =====================================================
    %% Execution
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph ExecutionFlow["Rollback Execution"]

        Relay["Relay Network"]
        Agent["BeaconLink Agent"]
        Runtime["Runtime Adapter"]
        Restore["Restore Previous State"]

    end

    Dispatch --> Relay
    Relay --> Agent
    Agent --> Runtime
    Runtime --> Restore

    %% =====================================================
    %% Verification
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Verification["Rollback Verification"]

        Verify["Health Verification"]
        Confirm["State Verification"]
        Reconcile["Reconciliation"]

    end

    Restore --> Verify
    Verify --> Confirm
    Confirm --> Reconcile

    %% =====================================================
    %% Completion
    %% =====================================================

    RollbackDecision{"Rollback Successful?"}

    Reconcile --> RollbackDecision

    RollbackComplete["Rollback Complete"]

    Manual["Manual Intervention"]

    RollbackDecision -->|Yes| RollbackComplete

    RollbackDecision -->|No| Manual

    %% =====================================================
    %% Audit & Events
    %% =====================================================

    Audit["Audit Log"]

    Events["Platform Events"]

    RollbackComplete --> Audit
    Manual --> Audit

    Audit --> Events

    %% =====================================================
    %% Continuous Reconciliation
    %% =====================================================

    Events --> Reconcile

    %% =====================================================
    %% Rollback Triggers
    %% =====================================================

    Triggers["Automatic Rollback Triggers

• Health Check Failure
• Readiness Failure
• Policy Violation
• Runtime Failure
• Drift Beyond Threshold
• Deployment Timeout
• Operator Cancellation"]

    Triggers -.-> Detect

    %% =====================================================
    %% Principles
    %% =====================================================

    Principles["Rollback Principles

• Immutable Revisions
• Automated Recovery
• Idempotent Operations
• Health-Gated Decisions
• Runtime Independent
• Fully Auditable
• Continuous Reconciliation"]

    Principles -.-> Rollback
    Principles -.-> Verification

